@NODE 1
@TITLE "PROGRAM INFO"

 Title  Search  makes  amigaguide  file  containing  all strings, which were
 followed  by  keyword "@TITLE" in source amigaguide file.  I use it to make
 indexes of my amigaguide files.

@ENDNODE

@NODE 2
@TITLE "HOW TO USE"

 Using TS is very easy. Watch a template:

        TS {in file} {out file}

 where:

        in file  = source  amigaguide,  which MUST contain any strings
                  starting by "@TITLE".        

        out file = destination index file.

@ENDNODE

